  <div class="featurette primary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="featurette-image" data-sr="scale up 50%">
          <%= image_tag 'icon_automate.png' %>
        </div>
        <div class="featurette-text" data-sr="enter bottom, hustle 50px">
          <h1>Automate Your Process</h1>
          <p class="lead">Software that runs your business</p>
          <p>
            Whether the task be menial or critical, automating all
            or a portion of your business process means gained
            efficiencies. That means <strong>BIG</strong> financial savings!
          </p>
          <p>
            Eliminate bottlenecks and free your workforce so they can spend
            more time concentrating on taking your company to the next level.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="featurette alternate">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="featurette-image" data-sr="enter left, hustle 50px, over 1.2s">
          <%= image_tag 'icon_integrate.png' %>
        </div>
        <div class="featurette-text" data-sr="enter right, hustle 50px, over 1.2s">
          <h1>Integrated Solutions</h1>
          <p class="lead">See for yourself</p>
          <p>
            We can help you create almost any sort of customized software you can think of,
            from <strong>CRM & HRM systems</strong> to <strong>e-commerce platforms</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Transform your business from a paper based system and harness your new
            digitally powered productivity, or prototype and create your
            new web application with us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="featurette primary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="featurette-image with-perspective" data-sr="spin 90deg, over 1.2s">
          <%= image_tag 'icon_responsive.png' %>
        </div>
        <div class="featurette-text" data-sr="enter top, hustle 50px, over 1.2s">
          <h1>Fully Responsive Webapps</h1>
          <p class="lead">From desktop to mobile</p>
          <p>
            We believe in building webapps that can be used
            in any screen size, from your laptop to your favourite
            smart phone.
          </p>
          <p>
            Ensure your site has top-notch <strong>SEO</strong> with mobile optimized
            applications, superb loading speeds and industry best practices from day one with us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="about-us-section">
